    Duplicatable, GenericRecord 

    public final class EscherDggRecord
extends EscherRecord
    This record defines the drawing groups used for a particular sheet.(此记录定义用于特定图纸的图形组。)

                                                int numShapedUsed)
        Add a new cluster(添加新群集)

        dgId - id of the drawing group (stored in the record options)(dgId -图形组的id（存储在记录选项中）)
        numShapedUsed - initial value of the numShapedUsed field(numShapedUsed -numShapedUsed字段的初始值)

      • addCluster

        public EscherDggRecord.FileIdCluster addCluster(int dgId,
                                                int numShapedUsed,
                                                boolean sort)
        Add a new cluster(添加新群集)
        Parameters:
        dgId - id of the drawing group (stored in the record options)(dgId -图形组的id（存储在记录选项中）)
        numShapedUsed - initial value of the numShapedUsed field(numShapedUsed -numShapedUsed字段的初始值)
        sort - if true then sort clusters by drawing group id.( In Excel the clusters are sorted but in PPT they are not)(排序-如果为真，则通过绘制组ID对集群进行排序。（在Excel中，集群是经过排序的，但在PPT中则不是）)
        Returns:
        the new EscherDggRecord.FileIdCluster(新的土方DggRecord. File Id集群)
